878
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:27,630
My throat went tight.

879
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,870
Thanks.

880
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:29,990
Yeah.

881
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,470
