901
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:11,310
My CPS case worker, my son's teacher,

902
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:12,950
the shelter director.

903
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:15,270
CPS case worker, told him the short

904
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,510
version.

905
