928
00:28:59,040 --> 00:29:01,310
6 weeks after the lockout, Jerome helped

929
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,990
me move our two duffel bags and three

930
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,590
boxes of donated stuff into the

931
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:05,830
apartment.

932
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:07,669
Mrs. Patterson dropped off dishes and

933
00:29:07,679 --> 00:29:08,950
