This is mine? Connor asked.

940
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:23,030
All yours.

941
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:24,990
He ran around it twice, touched the

942
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,430
walls like he couldn't believe they were

943
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,590
