986
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:50,830
"Case is closed," she said.

987
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:53,030
"You're employed, housing is stable,

988
00:30:53,040 --> 00:30:54,670
Connor's thriving.

989
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,630
No safety concerns."

990
