997
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,630
"He's always been difficult.

998
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,910
This is just another manipulation."

999
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:16,390
My father's. "We have rights. This is

1000
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:18,190
