1006
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:29,790
Closed the file. Put it in the cabinet

1007
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:31,070
under the sink behind the cleaning

1008
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:32,430
supplies.

1009
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:33,990
Not to forget.

1010
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:36,350
To remember what I'd survived.

1011
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:38,190
Two months after the lockout, Kyle

1012
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,990
