1013
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,750
First time seeing it.

1014
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:43,710
Brought pizza, played cards with Connor

1015
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,710
on the living room floor. Laughed when

1016
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:47,750
Connor beat him in a race.

1017
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:49,870
"Is Uncle Kyle staying?" Connor asked at

1018
