Kyle's eyes went wet.

1022
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:57,990
"Thanks."

1023
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:00,110
After Connor fell asleep, we sat on the

1024
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:01,710
