1038
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,470
Read through it one more time.

1039
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:29,230
My parents' version.

1040
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:30,710
My version.

1041
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,870
Mrs. Chen's version.

1042
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,390
Only one of those versions had a

1043
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,110
6-year-old shivering on a porch in a

1044
