blizzard.

1045
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:39,710
Put the file back in the cabinet.

1046
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:41,230
Two months ago, we'd been locked out

1047
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,950
with nowhere to go.

1048
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,630
Tonight, Connor was asleep in his own

1049
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:46,110
room in our apartment with food in the

1050
