1062
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:14,070
Connor was thriving.

1063
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:16,310
Straight A's and B's, three friends he

1064
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:18,390
talked about constantly, soccer on

1065
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,830
Saturdays that he loved even though he

1066
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,310
