1090
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:08,990
Sat down with him on the couch.

1091
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,110
"Do you want to go to Great-grandma's

1092
00:34:10,120 --> 00:34:11,389
funeral?"

1093
