He was cautious.

1094
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:15,349
"Will Grandma and Grandpa be there?"

1095
00:34:15,359 --> 00:34:16,590
"Yes."

1096
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:18,190
"Will they be mean?"

1097
00:34:18,200 --> 00:34:19,470
"I don't know.

1098
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,710
