1099
00:34:20,720 --> 00:34:22,669
Connor thought hard, chewing his bottom

1100
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:24,230
lip the way he did when making big

1101
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:25,669
decisions.

1102
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:28,270
"I don't want to go," he said finally.

1103
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,470
"Okay. You can stay with Jerome. I'll go

1104
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,990
