Dad's hardened.

1119
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:03,710
I didn't move, didn't approach.

1120
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,150
Just sat.

1121
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:07,390
Service was short, generic words about a

1122
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,150
woman I'd known but never been close to

1123
00:35:09,160 --> 00:35:10,470
because my parents had always kept

1124
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:12,230
distance between us.

1125
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:14,150
Like they'd been ashamed.

1126
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:16,550
Burial was outside in the cemetery, snow

1127
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:18,550
dusting the headstones, wind cutting

1128
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:20,030
through coats.

1129
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,550
People dispersed after the pastor

1130
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:22,830
