1141
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:39,750
"What did you tell her?"

1142
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,150
He shifted.

1143
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:42,670
Uncomfortable.

1144
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:44,750
"That you were going through something."

1145
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,150
"You mean you didn't tell her you locked

1146
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,590
me and Connor out in a blizzard?"

1147
00:35:48,600 --> 00:35:50,349
His jaw tightened. "We did what we

1148
00:35:50,359 --> 00:35:51,710
thought was right."

1149
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:52,870
"Then you have nothing to apologize

1150
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,830
for."

1151
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,110
Walked away.

1152
00:35:55,120 --> 00:35:56,430
He didn't follow.

1153
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:57,790
Got to my car.

1154
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:59,470
Reached for the door handle.

1155
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,830
Heard footsteps.

1156
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,990
My mother.

1157
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,830
Face red, crying.

1158
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:04,910
"Please.

1159
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,110
Can we talk?"

1160
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:07,270
Tired.

1161
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,830
Bone deep. Tired of this.

1162
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:11,270
"What's left to say?"

1163
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,630
"I miss Connor.

1164
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:13,990
I miss you."

1165
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,349
Felt the pull.

1166
00:36:15,359 --> 00:36:16,630
The old wound that wanted to believe

1167
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:18,510
maybe this time would be different.

1168
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,790
Stayed firm.

1169
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,510
"You called him trash, Mom.

1170
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:22,990
To his face."

1171
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,270
She sobbed.

1172
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,349
"I know.

1173
00:36:25,359 --> 00:36:26,790
I'm so sorry.

1174
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,110
I was angry.

1175
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,390
I didn't mean it."

1176
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,630
"You meant it.

1177
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:32,230
You've always resented him."

1178
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:33,630
"That's not true."

1179
00:36:33,640 --> 00:36:35,950
Pulled out my phone, opened email.

1180
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,150
"If you want any chance, here's what I

1181
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,310
need."

1182
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,590
She stared.

1183
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:40,630
"What?"

1184
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:41,950
"I'll email you."

1185
00:36:41,960 --> 00:36:43,270
"Conditions.

1186
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,710
Non-negotiable.

1187
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:46,430
You meet them or we're done.

1188
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,470
Forever."

1189
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,590
Drove home.

1190
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,190
Sat at the kitchen table.

1191
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:52,790
Typed out the email with Kyle CC'd.

1192
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:55,790
Subject. Conditions for contact.

1193
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:56,710
One.

1194
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:58,910
Both parents attend family therapy.

1195
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,230
Provide proof.

1196
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:01,190
Two.

1197
00:37:01,200 --> 00:37:02,950
Written apology to Connor.

1198
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:04,910
I approve before you send.

1199
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:05,950
Three.

1200
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,310
No comments about my parenting,

1201
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:09,190
finances, or past.

1202
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:10,190
Four.

1203
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:12,230
Supervised visits only.

1204
00:37:12,240 --> 00:37:13,710
Public places.

1205
00:37:13,720 --> 00:37:15,310
One hour maximum.

1206
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:16,430
Five.

1207
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:18,110
One violation equals permanent no

1208
00:37:18,120 --> 00:37:19,430
contact.

1209
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:21,510
Stared at it for 5 minutes.

1210
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:23,630
Finger hovering over send.

1211
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:25,150
Sent.

1212
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:27,790
Three days later, two responses.

1213
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,910
My father's came first.

1214
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,950
"These demands are insulting.

1215
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:33,750
We are your parents.

1216
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:35,430
When you're ready to act like an adult,

1217
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,830
call us."

1218
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,430
Deleted it.

1219
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:40,710
My mother's came an hour later.

1220
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:42,910
"Your father doesn't speak for me.

1221
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:45,070
I'm starting therapy this week."

1222
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:47,510
Attached the appointment confirmation.

1223
00:37:47,520 --> 00:37:49,470
"I'm writing Connor's letter.

1224
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:51,510
I'll send you a draft first.

1225
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:52,990
Please.

1226
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,750
I want to try."

1227
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,950
Opened the attachment.

1228
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:59,230
Real therapist, real appointment,

1229
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:01,390
scheduled for next Tuesday.

1230
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,910
Called Kyle.

1231
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,870
Read him both emails.

1232
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,390
"What are you going to do?" he asked.

1233
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,950
"I don't know yet.

1234
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:11,150
Part of me wants to believe her.

1235
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,750
And the other part?"

1236
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:14,670
"Remembers every time she chose him over

1237
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:15,710
me."

1238
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:18,390
Year later, Connor turned 7.

1239
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:20,870
Small birthday party in our apartment.

1240
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:23,590
Balloons, cheap decorations, cake from

1241
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:25,790
the grocery store bakery. Jerome came

1242
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,230
with his son.

1243
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:28,710
Mrs. Patterson brought a card and a

1244
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:29,870
book.

1245
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:32,150
Mr. Torres, our landlord, dropped off a

1246
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:33,510
gift card.

1247
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:35,430
Kyle drove in from Boston with a remote

1248
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:38,150
control car that Connor screamed over.

1249
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,670
My mother came.

1250
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:41,950
Supervised, one hour, on her best

1251
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:43,270
behavior.

1252
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:45,550
She'd been to therapy for 8 months. Sent

1253
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:47,270
me proof every week.

1254
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,870
Wrote Connor a letter I'd approved after

1255
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,470
three drafts.

1256
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:53,190
Visited twice supervised before today.

1257
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:54,790
Short visits.

1258
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,510
Careful visits.

1259
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:58,030
Her learning how to be a grandmother

1260
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,830
without being cruel.

1261
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:02,030
My father refused therapy, refused to

1262
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,550
apologize, refused everything. Wasn't

1263
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:06,030
invited.

1264
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:08,590
Mom brought a LEGO set. The exact one

1265
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:10,310
Connor had mentioned once three visits

1266
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:11,470
ago.

1267
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:13,670
He opened it, looked at her, said

1268
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:15,670
thanks, Grandma, with politeness but not

1269
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:16,830
warmth.

1270
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:19,590
She stayed for cake. Helped clean up.

1271
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,550
Hugged me before leaving.

1272
00:39:21,560 --> 00:39:22,990
"Thank you for this chance," she

1273
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,230
whispered.

1274
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:25,510
Nodded.

1275
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:27,310
Didn't say you're welcome.

1276
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,870
Wasn't there yet.

1277
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:30,550
That night, Connor climbed into bed with

1278
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:33,150
his new LEGO set on his nightstand.

1279
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:34,750
"Is Grandma going to visit again?" he

1280
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,910
asked.

1281
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:36,870
"Maybe.

1282
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:38,630
If she keeps trying."

1283
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:40,270
"What about Grandpa?"

1284
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:43,150
"No, buddy. Not unless he changes.

1285
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:44,990
And I don't think he will.

1286
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,550
Connor yawned.

1287
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:47,870
Okay.

1288
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:50,430
Fell asleep 2 minutes later.

1289
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,990
I sat in the living room with the lights

1290
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,870
off, looking at the apartment we'd built

1291
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:55,230
from nothing.

1292
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:57,590
Second-hand furniture, donated dishes,

1293
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:59,550
walls that needed paint.

1294
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:00,870
But ours.

1295
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,070
Safe.

1296
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:03,550
Stable.

1297
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:04,750
Used to think forgiveness meant

1298
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:06,830
pretending it never happened.

1299
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,270
That family meant loyalty no matter

1300
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,390
what.

1301
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,470
Connor taught me different.

1302
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:13,430
Forgiveness without accountability is

1303
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:16,150
just permission to hurt you again.

1304
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:17,950
Mom was trying.

1305
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,670
Actually trying.

1306
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:21,790
Therapy, apologies, showing up and

1307
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,150
behaving.

1308
00:40:23,160 --> 00:40:24,630
Dad wasn't.

1309
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:26,390
Refused to admit fault, refused to

1310
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:28,550
change, still believed he'd done nothing

1311
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,750
wrong.

1312
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,990
And I'd learned to tell the difference.

1313
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:34,310
Connor was asleep in his own room.

1314
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,870
In our apartment.

1315
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,350
Safe.

1316
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,790
Not because my parents finally loved

1317
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,750
him, but because I'd chosen him over

1318
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,310
their approval.

1319
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:45,120
That was everything.
